item.title: I give out cookies. Help me
item.dc:creator: @roguex roguex
item.description:
@roguex wrote:

well there is 2 “try{”'s so there needs to be 2 “catch”'s or “finnaly”'s

Example;

myFunction = function () { 
 trace("this is myFunction"); 
}; 
try { 
 myInterval = setInterval(this, "myFunction", 1000); 
 throw new Error("my error"); 
} 
catch (myError:Error) { 
 trace("error caught: "+myError); 
} 
finally { 
 clearInterval(myInterval); 
 trace("error is cleared"); 
}
